2026-02-03DNDNational Defence ActAppointment of a part-time member of the Military Police Complaints CommissionAppointment of Pascal Lévesque of Québec, Quebec, who is not an officer or non-commissioned member of the Canadian Forces, nor an employee of the Department of National Defence, to be a part-time member of the Military Police Complaints Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years.N/A
subject: Appointment of a part-time member of the Military Police Complaints Commission
precis: Appointment of Pascal Lévesque of Québec, Quebec, who is not an officer or non-commissioned member of the Canadian Forces, nor an employee of the Department of National Defence, to be a part-time member of the Military Police Complaints Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years.
